race.description: Tabtouch Past The Post Payouts (Bm58+) Handicap
race.comment: SNIPPETY LEGEND (2) closed off strongly last start to get up for third here. Goes well at this journey with two wins and two placings from five starts and looks a top chance. BONNY ROCK (5) showed good early speed and led throughout to score by a nose last start over 1200m at Bunbury. Sure to measure up again. LEADING TADDY (4) settled well back from a wide draw last time then wound up strongly to finish fourth over 1200m at this track. Kept coming and the extra ground looks a big plus. SPARKLE CORNER (1) improved sharply last time out to score by a head over 1200m at this track a week-and-a-half ago. Likely to be there at the finish again.
